;################################################### DISCONTINUED
@Node "1_Discontinued" "Read this!"

  @{b}@{u}AMIGAGUIDE DOCS DISCONTINUED@{uu}@{ub}

  The  AmigaGuide  documentation for @{i}Trinity Player@{ui} has been discontinued.
  Part  of the reason for this is that doing the ASCII "art" for the GUIs'
  was a major pain in the arse.

  For  this reason, I have decided to create HTML docs for @{i}Trinity Player@{ui},
  as it is (almost) perfectly suited to text with graphical elements.

  So,  only  the  HTML  docs  will  have  the latest information, and this
  AmigaGuide  file  won't be updated and soon will be phased out of the @{i}TP@{ui}
  archive.
@EndNode

